cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.MA 

The paper deals with reinforcement learning and recommendation systems for online advertising, which are topics that are commonly studied in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures (cs.DS), and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). However, given that the paper focuses on the application of these techniques to online advertising, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
